    <string name="output_hint">
        Please place your finger on the device\'s camera, covering the flash as well. After
        10 seconds, you can export the results through the menu.
        \n\nThis utility works by measuring the amount of red it sees through the camera, and
        attempting to detect the fluctuations.
        \nIt works better in a darkened room, and when the pressure on the camera is constant.
        \nIf there are multiple cameras on your device, make sure that your finger covers the entire
        field of view in the small viewfinder.
        \nOnce the measurement is complete, it can be exported or repeated through the menu.
    </string>
